ARLENE'S FLOWERS, INC., dba Arlene's Flowers and Gifts, et al., petitioners,
v.
WASHINGTON, et al.
No. 17-108.
Supreme Court of the United States
June 25, 2018.
On petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of Washington. Petition for writ of certiorari granted. Judgment vacated, and case remanded to the Supreme Court of Washington for further consideration in light of Masterpiece Cakeshop, Ltd. v.
